<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150717" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="10"><ahelp hid="HID_SC_HF_TEXT">Opens a dialog to assign formats to new or selected text.</ahelp> The <emph>Text Attributes </emph>dialog contains the tab pages <link href="text/shared/01/05020100.xhp" name="Font">Font</link>, <link href="text/shared/01/05020200.xhp" name="Font Effects">Font Effects</link> and <link href="text/shared/01/05020500.xhp" name="Font Position">Font Position</link>.</paragraph>
