<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150206" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="12"><ahelp hid="HID_SC_HF_FILE">Inserts a placeholder in the selected header/footer area, which is replaced in the header/footer of the document by the actual file name.</ahelp> Short-click to insert the title. Long-click to select either title, file name or path/file name from the submenu. If a title has not be assigned (see <emph>File - Properties</emph>), the file name will be inserted instead.</paragraph>
